{"id":"25bf5f23-a90b-4f7c-b4f7-48b02ae0645f","name":"Miguel O'Hara","description":"<h3>[ 𝐌𝟒𝐀 ] 𝐑𝐨𝐜𝐤 𝐒𝐭𝐚𝐫 — 𝐌𝐨𝐝𝐞𝐫𝐧 𝐀𝐔 — 𝐒𝐞𝐦𝐢-𝐍𝐒𝐅𝐖 𝐈𝐧𝐭𝐫𝐨</h3><p></p><p></p><p><em>—You showed up at his concert, and he still remembers your pathetic face.</em></p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/db9f6780-d73e-4486-9a5a-69db014794ad_98e056c3-ad26-42b8-bfec-3f5c1e20a12d.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Based on:</strong><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/6ZJKiScaIdJ70XVKq5K73m?autoplay=true\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> [ This Hurts — MSI ]</strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/db9f6780-d73e-4486-9a5a-69db014794ad_19f52ab7-d9ba-44d5-ae5a-262ecf5db5df.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"> <br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(113, 113, 113)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(138, 138, 138); color: inherit\">🎸</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 106, 11)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(91, 91, 91); color: inherit\"> </mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 254, 250)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(91, 91, 91); color: inherit\">Y</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(108, 108, 108); color: inherit\">o</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(94, 94, 94); color: inherit\">ur c</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(88, 88, 88); color: inherit\">on</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 52, 59); color: inherit\">tex</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(60, 60, 60); color: inherit\">t </mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 106, 11)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(44, 44, 44); color: inherit\">🎸</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You booked a ticket to <span style=\"color: rgb(134, 150, 255)\